t><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/ubrelkeryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brelkeryn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Primal Ooze</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#871F78>(6/3/02 4:34:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1745.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Recommended Beastlord Starting Stats?</span><hr size=1> For fun, I was planning on starting a Beastlord.  It seems that Iksar is a popular racial choice for the end game.  How would you recommend distributing the starting stats for such a character?<br>
<br>
