Brelk <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/ubrelkeryn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Brelkeryn</A> at: 6/3/02 4:37:06 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub115.ezboard.com/ugoraminspiritbane.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goramin Spiritbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>mewling</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#871F78>(6/3/02 4:50:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub115.ezboard.com/feqbeastlordfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1745.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Recommended Beastlord Starting Stats?</span><hr size=1> As an iksar go all STA, its low enough as it is. <p><img border="3" src="http://www.freenorrath.com/images/bio/goramin.gif" width="200" height="300"></p><A HREF="http://www.freenorrath.com/roster/bios.asp?member=goramin">Goramin Spiritbane</A>
